<div class="col-md-12">
    <p>
        Every Individual Is Fond Of Shopping And Meghalaya Is Able To Satisfy Everyone When It Comes To Shopping. Of All The Places In Meghalaya, Shillong Is The Most Visited Place. Visitors Coming To Shillong Can Shop In The Busy Police Bazaar And Bara Bazaar Area. There Are Few Shopping Malls In Shillong Which Includes Reliance Ttrendz, Vishal Mega Mart, Glory’s Plaza And Dreamland Arcade.  One Can Also Explore Meghalaya’s Crowded Markets For Trendy Souvenirs.

    </p>
    <p>
        <b>Must Buy From Meghalaya<br />
Shawls
</b><br />
    </p><p>
            Meghalaya Is Cold For Most Part Of The Year And Therefore You Can Find Variety Of Warm Clothes In The Markets Of Meghalaya. The Shawls Which You Can Find In Meghalaya Are Extremely Beautiful. You Can Find Naga And Manipuri Shawls In Almost All The Shops In The Markets. Most Of The Shops Also Sells  Woolen Manipuri Lungis.    </p><p>
    </p><p>
    <b>
        Scottish Dress Materials
    </b><br />
    </p><p>
            You Can Also Find Beautiful Dress Material In The Shops Which You Can Make Them Into Shirts, Skirts And Jackets. These Dress Material Are Extremely Warm And Beautiful. While You Can Find Number Of ‘Dress-Material’ In Meghalaya, But The Best One Is Hanumanbux Located Opposite Dreamland Cinema In Police Bazar, Shillong For The Variety They Keep. The Price Are Also Extremely Reasonable (About Rs 250 A Meter).    </p><p>
    </p>
    <p><b>Khasi Scrub</b><br />
    </p>
    <p>Khasi Scrub Is Something Which You Must Defiantly Buy. This Is Something Unique And You Will Never Find In Big Cities. Khasi Scrub Can Be Found Almost Everywhere. The Price Of This Scrub Is Rs 50. 
    </p>
    
    <p><b>Food Items</b><br />
    </p><p>
            Meghalaya Is A Place For Those Who Loves To Try Different Food Items.  Bara Bazaar Is Known For Selling Fruits, Vegetables And Spices. Meghalaya Is Also Famous For Momos. If You Want To Try Some Local Cuisine Then You Must Defiantly Try Jadoh.
    </p>
    <p>
        <b>  Handloom And Handicraft Items</b><br />
    </p><p>
          
            The Shops In Meghalaya Are Also Known For Selling Handloom And Handicraft Items. Some Items Which Are Available In The Shops Include Endi Silk Shawls, Decorative Items, Artistic Wood Carving And Many More.
